<MS2<TURDo you understand the
splendor of this?<WAI0023
Do you?!<WAI0023<CLRI doubt you do!<WAI0022<CLRThen allow me to
explain it...<WAI0022<CLR
In a special lecture!!<WAI0021<CLRYou've come at a
splendid time.<WAI0021
Here, they're all yours!<WAI0020<CLROh, no, no,
don't thank me.<WAI0020
Have fun, you three.<WAI0019<CLRMy body may be wrecked,
but my consciousness has never
been more distinct.<WAI0018<CLRIt feels as if I have become
a superman!<WAI0017<CLR
Gyaaahhh!<MYB0220<WAI0016<CLRThe...<WAI0015
the power...<WAI0014<CLR
I can't control it!!!<WAI0013<CLRWhy, yes.<WAI0012
I am the Doctor.<WAI0011<CLRAnd from now on, I am
your new leader.<WAI0010<CLRPleased to make your
acquaintance.<WAI0008<CLRThe power of the Red Crystal
is wondrous indeed.<WAI0006
